title: Songs Without Words -City of Prague Philharmonic Orchestra
description:
Songs Without Words, the stunning brand new album from Classic FM.
This album features all your favourite pop songs as you have never heard them before, including sensational arrangements of:' Yellow', `Closest Thing to Crazy' and `Fields of Gold'.

Julian Lloyd Webber, Craig Ogden and Simon Mulligan are amongst the line-up of featured artists who contribute to this special album.
These beautiful new tracks have been exclusively recorded for this album and are not available anywhere else.

Track Listings
1. Yellow
2. My Heart Will Go On
3. The Closest Thing To Crazy - Simon Mulligan
4. You Raise Me Up - Fiona McCapra, City of Prague Philharmonic Orchestra
5. Fields Of Gold - Craig Ogden, City of Prague Philharmonic Orchestra
6. Sorry Seems To Be The Hardest Word - Pete Whyman, City of Prague Philharmonic   Orchestra
7. Somewhere Only We Know
8. Save The Best For Last - Julian Lloyd Webber, City of Prague Philharmonic Orchestra
9. With Or Without You
10. Something Inside So Strong - Emma Johnson, City of Prague Philharmonic Orchestra
11. Right Here Waiting
12. Life On Mars
